She on Nick's jock.

02:13.842 --> 02:16.761
-Party don't start till 9:00, so...
-What time is it now?

02:17.053 --> 02:19.764
Bro, I know you see the watch.
Why you ask him?

02:19.848 --> 02:22.684
-Come on--
-Oh, man, careful with that!

02:23.101 --> 02:23.935
[laughter]

02:24.018 --> 02:27.021
Oh, y'all real funny. Y'all got jokes.
I wanna see... Where y'all watches?

02:27.105 --> 02:28.064
-Oh, shit.
-What's that?

02:28.148 --> 02:29.858
Tell me they ain't coming
to Sharene's party.

02:29.941 --> 02:32.026
<i>-</i>I don't know, bro. What's going on?
-[rowdy yelling]

02:32.152 --> 02:33.820
