02:53.506 --> 02:54.716
<i>♪ I got a habit ♪</i>

02:54.799 --> 02:56.676
<i>♪ You can't solve it, silly rabbit ♪</i>

02:57.218 --> 02:59.512
-Yo, let's go Saturday.
-Saturday it is.

02:59.762 --> 03:01.598
Yo, is that Deondre coming for us?

03:02.182 --> 03:03.641
[man] Yo, Kane!

03:04.267 --> 03:06.811
No, that's Al Morris. He cool.

03:06.895 --> 03:08.897
Come on, man.
We're going to the park. Let's move.

03:16.613 --> 03:18.907
