-I'm hungry now.

03:20.283 --> 03:22.493
Okay, I said, "Baby girl, you hungry?"
You said, "No."
-I know what I said, Korey.
-"No."

03:24.871 --> 03:27.207
-There you go, taking all my food.
-[man 1] Yo!

03:27.665 --> 03:29.959
-Pollo! Let's go, we're going to the park!
-[man 2] Let's go!

03:30.460 --> 03:32.128
Come on! Let's go, right now! Let's go!

03:32.212 --> 03:33.713
-I thought you was hungry.
-Come on!

03:33.796 --> 03:36.132
