03:56.110 --> 03:57.070
[man] Hey, yo!

03:58.112 --> 03:59.989
Yo, what do you think they're doing?

04:00.323 --> 04:01.824
I don't know. Let's go ball.

04:03.576 --> 04:05.745
Man, I'll see you.
I've got a game waiting.

